imdb.plot outline: Joe Rogan is joined by friends such as Ari Shaffir, Duncan Trussell, Joey "Coco" Diaz, Bryan Callen, and Eddie Bravo to discuss topics ranging from chimpanzees ingesting hallucinogens to chimpanzees ripping your face off. Train by day, Joe Rogan podcast by night, all day.
imdb.title: The Joe Rogan Experience
plot: Joe Rogan hosts long form conversations with friends and guests that include comedians, actors, musicians, MMA instructors and commentators, authors and artists.

Joe Rogan is joined by friends such as Ari Shaffir, Duncan Trussell, Joey "Coco" Diaz, Bryan Callen, and Eddie Bravo to discuss topics ranging from chimpanzees ingesting hallucinogens to chimpanzees ripping your face off. Train by day, Joe Rogan podcast by night, all day.::Don Doarderty

The JRE takes you down a path of stepping away from all of your preconceived notions of dozens, if not hundreds of subjects. Dive into the world of semi famous comediens, learn from the knowledge of doctors and professors, become motivated by hunter friends or an ex navy seal. Take away powerful, soul burning rants by the man himself, or relax, have a drink and watch a fight with friends. The glory of the JRE lies in the variety of information and guests who always bring a great conversation to the table.::Aaron Martinez
